2nd July 2016 ITV4
11:00 to 16:30 Stage 1

Gary Imlach and Chris Boardman present live coverage of stage one which is a ride through history. It goes northwards across the Cherbourg Peninsula from the UNESCO World Heritage Site at Mont-Saint-Michel, to Utah Beach, one of the settings of the Normandy landings on D-Day. Commentary by David Millar and Ned Boulting with Daniel Friebe reporting from the roadside.
